description:
I'm headed to Gordan Ramsay Burger for dinner in this video and I'm going to  be giving you my thoughts on the meal from appetizers to dessert. Gordon Ramsay is my favorite celebrity chef and I'm always happy to eat at his restaurants. 

Please like, share and subscribe!

Gordon Ramsay Burger
(A): 3667 S Las Vegas Blvd, Las Vegas, NV 89109
(P): (702) 785-5462

Filmed on a Samsung Galaxy S21 Ultra
Sound by RODE Wireless Go2
Music from Epidemic Sound
Edited with Wondershare Filmora 11 Information regarding hours, offerings, and prices in this video are subject to change at the discretion of restaurant operators.
